{"tid":1833882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(食蝙蝠？？) 陳肇始：內地專家相信新型冠狀病毒肺炎與蝙蝠有關","createTime":"2020-01-22T06:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T07:35:53.000Z","uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b62486c4fb3696e74967b7c5bfc7182fe92149e6","tid":1833882,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始出席網台節目後說，內地專家相信新型冠狀病毒肺炎與蝙蝠有關，內地仍在調查動物宿主。她說，從流行病學及應對防控而言，最重要是知道病毒如何確診及測試，特區政府現掌握確診者的臨床醫治方法及用藥。<br />\n<br />\n對於澳門出現確診個案，她說香港與澳門有通報機制，相信衞生防護中心已有工作應對，現時未有最新資訊。<br />\n<br />\n她又說政府有權隔離確診病人，早前政府已在《預防及控制疾病條例》中加入新型冠狀病毒，故有法律基礎做隔離和通報。私家及公立醫院醫生發現個案時，會立即通報衞生防護中心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504163-20200122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504163-20200122.htm&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=1d29a087\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504163-20200122.htm&h=5b356e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504163-20200122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e4fb3aa053e4a5fa9e959a8e791c47bae721afc8","tid":1833882,"uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"快d放無國界醫生上武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270fa682be6efc9072368fc195718eb9bc1a3696","tid":1833882,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1vP1f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1vP1f7.png&h=93792b16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f1d140895724b9b7772936c1fed063c3752c8b4","tid":1833882,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"利申先 我估架咋<br />\n<br />\n2003年果子狸被batman感染<br />\n支那人食果子狸先中SARS<br />\n<br />\n所以陳xx就斷鳩估今次係batman傳染竹鼠"},{"pid":"2b90c06d0a